{"tid":1123404,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"獨孤九劍 vs 天山折梅手 邊個好打啲?","createTime":"2019-04-24T12:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T13:06:47.000Z","uid":39866,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5ffcd8f31ad4d4787952b61372b7614b1b017650","tid":1123404,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"獨孤九劍<br />\n分做九大部分，完全無招，視對方招式而定，遇強則強。有進無退，招招都是進攻，攻敵之不得不守。<br />\n<br />\n天山折梅手<br />\n天山折梅手共包括三路掌法，三路擒拿法，一共六路武功，天下任何招數武功，都能自行化在這六路折梅手之中。<br />\n<br />\n獨孤九劍破盡天下，而天山折梅手號稱拳腳版九劍，同樣bug到爆炸，夠竟邊個好打啲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獨孤九劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天山折梅手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf6e8bf3b4fd9e5460f8fe82af76c135858b3aa","tid":1123404,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"互打九劍贏<br />\n打其他人就折梅手實用啲<br />\n<br />\nbetween 又多個金庸post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50161e6d6412648733a2e6bcef9a2f15fdbe15db","tid":1123404,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"你老母最好打 日日俾人輪住砌都原好無缺 <br />\n練左九陰+九陽？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日撚日係咁撚樣九劍vs玄劍 楊vs張 好撚煩<br />\nVs夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baf054c6790cd77f8b0fce6028455074b2fcb07","tid":1123404,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:51:39.000Z","msg":"拳頭交九劍輸 因為無劍 此post已完"},{"pid":"afe5fdf3baa5d1552eb38b1abfd56833853fc1bd","tid":1123404,"uid":75095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"九劍擋核彈都得"},{"pid":"fbcb54ebc4bd012c1d2652314022ccf2d5922ba4","tid":1123404,"uid":104980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"獨孤九劍唔用內力 天山折梅手睇用者功力"},{"pid":"b0aabfc930b7e50f8e9ce5ecc7c6d